13. Cheat Sheet
reshape() -> Change shape
flatten() -> Copy
ravel() -> View
T -> Transpose
zeros() -> Zeros
ones() -> Ones
eye() -> Identity Matrix
arange() -> Range
linspace() -> Even spacing
rand() -> Decimal random
randint() -> Integer random
